179  private static final Map<? extends SearchParameter, Term> ARRAY_STRING_TERMS =
180      ImmutableMap.<OccurrenceSearchParameter, Term>builder()
181          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.NETWORK_KEY, GbifInternalTerm.networkKey)
182          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.DWCA_EXTENSION, GbifInternalTerm.dwcaExtension)
183          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.IDENTIFIED_BY_ID, DwcTerm.identifiedByID)
184          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.RECORDED_BY_ID, DwcTerm.recordedByID)
185          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.DATASET_ID, DwcTerm.datasetID)
186          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.DATASET_NAME, DwcTerm.datasetName)
187          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.OTHER_CATALOG_NUMBERS, DwcTerm.otherCatalogNumbers)
188          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.RECORDED_BY, DwcTerm.recordedBy)
189          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.IDENTIFIED_BY, DwcTerm.identifiedBy)
190          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.PREPARATIONS, DwcTerm.preparations)
191          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.SAMPLING_PROTOCOL, DwcTerm.samplingProtocol)
192          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.PROJECT_ID, GbifTerm.projectId)
193          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.GEOREFERENCED_BY, DwcTerm.georeferencedBy)
194          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.HIGHER_GEOGRAPHY, DwcTerm.higherGeography)
195          .put(OccurrenceSearchParameter.ASSOCIATED_SEQUENCES, DwcTerm.associatedSequences)
196          .build();
197
198  private static final Map<SearchParameter, Term> DENORMED_TERMS = Collections.emptyMap();
199
200  @Override
201  public Term term(SearchParameter searchParameter) {
202    return PARAM_TO_TERM.get(searchParameter);
203  }
204
205  @Override
206  public boolean isArray(SearchParameter searchParameter) {
207    return ARRAY_STRING_TERMS.containsKey(searchParameter);
208  }
209
210  @Override
211  public Term getTermArray(SearchParameter searchParameter) {
212    return ARRAY_STRING_TERMS.get(searchParameter);
213  }
214
215  @Override
216  public boolean isDenormedTerm(SearchParameter searchParameter) {
217    return DENORMED_TERMS.containsKey(searchParameter);
218  }
219
220  @Override
221  public SearchParameter getDefaultGadmLevel() {
222    return OccurrenceSearchParameter.GADM_LEVEL_0_GID;
223  }
224
225  @Override
226  public boolean includeNullInPredicate(SimplePredicate<SearchParameter> predicate) {
227    return OccurrenceSearchParameter.DISTANCE_FROM_CENTROID_IN_METERS == predicate.getKey()
228        && (predicate instanceof GreaterThanOrEqualsPredicate
229            || predicate instanceof GreaterThanPredicate);
230  }
